        "body": "## Changes (Feb 16 - Feb 23)\n\n### What's New\n- **Improved UI & CSS**: Enhanced the overall look and feel of the Streamlit application with better styling and layout\n- **Graph Visualization**: Improved graph visuals — better sizing, cleaner aesthetics, and removed emojis from charts\n- **Batch Prediction Support**: Added ability to upload CSV files for bulk churn prediction with risk distribution charts\n- **Model Evaluation Metrics**: Added accuracy, precision, recall, F1 score, confusion matrix, and ROC curve when true labels are available\n- **Download Results**: Users can now download prediction results as CSV\n- **Requirements File**: Added `requirements.txt` for easy dependency installation\n\n### Files Changed\n- `app.py` — Main application with all enhancements\n- `requirements.txt` — New file listing project dependencies",
